{"tid":1293773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲交稅養班閪狗打人?","createTime":"2019-07-07T16:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T17:07:00.000Z","uid":109032,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"192ed5291b8d706c73e9ea9f20f2678e71e7951d","tid":1293773,"uid":109032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"不合作運動要包括埋唔交稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3bd516cb6b8a25cbccb599f05e77a57a4600613","tid":1293773,"uid":132175,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:47:56.000Z","msg":"一係分20幾張支票 寄過去"},{"pid":"dd6a78236503c222641b0afb4e6d0844ab054983","tid":1293773,"uid":55355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:07:00.000Z","msg":"純粹發夢<br />\n如果成立個我哋自己既稅局？（類似眾籌）<br />\n納稅人唔再交稅俾政府 instead 俾我哋<br />\n當然成件事要有好高既透明度<br />\n我哋自己決定咩緊急部門繼續有錢（e.g. 公立醫院，消防，民生有關既服務）<br />\n咩部門唔會有錢（黑警、政府）<br />\n咁起碼可以解決唔交稅會影響民生既論調<br />\n又可以我哋拎番主動權<br />\n<br />\n不過好多technical issue要解決，例如邊個決定點用啲錢（簡單啲黎講就係一個政權）。 而呢個基本上係可以睇成成立臨時政府第一步。"}]}